description:
| Artificial intelligence promises great value. The technology is mostly
  understood only by few, yet still unexplainable even for experts.
| In this talk I'll present how to narrow the hype down to real value
  explainable to everyone in your organisation - without the math.

Slides can you downloaded at http://bit.ly/ai-executives-data-litteracy-
europython
title: Explaining AI to Managers 👨‍💼🤖👩‍💼
